query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sms_health_tips (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  tip_content TEXT NOT NULL,
  category VARCHAR(100),
  is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
  last_sent_at TIMESTAMP,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
